name: B.I.G Steel Blue Work Boots
description:
Steel Blue are the Boots of choice here @ B.I.G . 
Sizes-3 - 16 UK and Half sizes 5 1/2-13 1/2 .


This boot has been designed for the Oil and Gas Industry,  Key features of the Torquay Black Nitrile (627539) include;

•Spark Ignition Proof 
•Abrasion resistant toe guard
•Water and corrosion resistant
•Its wider fitting and lighter than standard steel caps
•The cleat pattern of the sole has been designed to provide excellent slip resistance whilst still disbursing petroleum mud
•Strong Ankle Support
•The Quick Release zip allows easy access on and off in an emergency 
•Finally you can walk through airports without having to take your boots off
•100% Comfort Guaranteed


Give Steve Nash a call on 0488121178 for all you individual and company needs.
